{"tid":1741710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咁多位 今日20號啦 仲有4日 一個上熱門既區選post都無？","createTime":"2019-11-20T12:41:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T14:37:08.000Z","uid":41873,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6f57d1ce9307e65cdf3a4a18316ed8837ce7426c","tid":1741710,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:41:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">究竟你地係咪想贏</span></span></strong><br />\n今日已經有大量親戚問我要投俾邊個 <br />\n我又驚答錯佢地 <br />\n想請全能既連仔馬上出手總結下每個站要投邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋 我想講樣好恐怖既野俾你地既<br />\n今日我有個朋友收到個電話 叫佢要投俾邊個<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">對方仲要知道我朋友住邊度 叫咩名</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n真人真事 絕無老作<br />\n所以我真係想大家呢幾日真係要專心搞好個區選先<br />\n<br />\n當然早上晨運要繼續<br />\n但真係要推區選post啦 得番<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4日</span></span></strong>炸咁多位！！"},{"pid":"2ebf30ef2c65106d94768005fe3c7102793a378c","tid":1741710,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:43:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77b7191eafb40478d9943c42733598f574543ef0","tid":1741710,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:43:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75d7266166ed1ac6c8ddd11c60259e1bf9d566ef","tid":1741710,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:44:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8a5527ff13909a6bca4c0d96e7cc5bd0475f4b7","tid":1741710,"uid":315880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gh3hcEu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgh3hcEu.png&h=5606655a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足聽日唔好再遲到 5AM有早冇遲呀香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫手推下行動post啦 ！！！<br />\n好多人都唔知聽日繼續三罷堵路呀！！<br />\n